{"tid":2511183,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"如果一路唔俾菲傭入境香港 會唔會樓爆","createTime":"2021-04-30T16:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T17:59:09.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10692288d4c4a78ced55ed136deafdb59a498913","tid":2511183,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:53:32.000Z","msg":"菲律賓航班停晒 啲外傭供應斷咗一隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔同以前 而家啲樓價要兩公婆一齊返工先供得起 屋企有老人家或小朋友要照顧咪焗住搵工人湊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一冇工人就要是但一個辭職照顧屋企 到時層樓未必供得起 又或者本來買得起變成買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家初初禁梗係仲有得gogogo 如果菲律賓航班停多排 甚至連印尼都停埋 新嘅黎唔到市面越來越少外傭供應 請唔到就要辭職 到時會唔會樓爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗諗吓真係有機會 如果唔係點解林奠當初死都唔肯禁菲律賓啲航班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73d88f342983c513e71d33f4e20abc74ea46f13","tid":2511183,"uid":232660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"會有好多獨留兒童在家就真。"},{"pid":"57e62fb9306b2707e57767af27d068c9627b0276","tid":2511183,"uid":39206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:54:56.000Z","msg":"會多左好多本地工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd74126fda9ed0c32a6512b80d84c9d2717512f0","tid":2511183,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b73d88f342983c513e71d33f4e20abc74ea46f13","tid":2511183,"uid":232660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"會有好多獨留兒童在家就真。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"黎字派點會做犯法野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3400cf4611958253a792262284a2755a94ca108d","tid":2511183,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e62fb9306b2707e57767af27d068c9627b0276","tid":2511183,"uid":39206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco